# Design System (required)

When editing UI, layout, colors, typography, spacing, or visual components in
`apps/yggdrasill` or `apps/yggdrasill_manager`, **first read**
[`docs/design-system.md`](../../docs/design-system.md) in full and follow it.

## Mandatory workflow

1. Read `docs/design-system.md` (checklist §0).
2. Build UI in **Preview only** — use the correct app folder:
   `design_preview/yggdrasill/` (learning app), `design_preview/m5/` (M5 UI),
   or `apps/yggdrasill_manager/.../design_preview/yggdrasill_manager/`.
   Do not mix apps in one preview file.
3. Do **not** edit production `*_screen.dart` until the customer confirms the
   Preview (Hot Reload review).
4. After approval: copy UI widget tree only; keep logic changes minimal and
   separate.

## Do not

- Add new HEX colors, fonts, radius, or spacing values not listed in the doc.
- Invent new widgets when §5 catalog components fit.
- Mix legacy (`#1F1F1F` shell) and new teal (`kDlg*`) palettes against §2.4.
- Change Provider/API/`onTap` business logic in the same pass as visual tweaks.
- Redesign from screenshots alone without functional context.

## Reuse first

- Colors: `dialog_tokens.dart` (`kDlg*`), existing `_rs*` / Theme constants.
- Widgets: `YggDialogSectionHeader`, `YggDialogFilterChip`, `PillTabSelector`,
  `CustomTabBar`, `CustomNavigationRail`, `DarkPanelRoute`, `showAppSnackBar`.

## After changes

Add one line to §10 (changelog) in `docs/design-system.md`.

## Prompt template

```text
docs/design-system.md를 먼저 읽고 준수해.
Preview 목업만 만들고, 프로덕션 화면은 건드리지 마.
문서의 토큰과 §5 컴포넌트만 사용해.
```
